00:25:47,614 --> 00:25:48,474
they were on the right track.

479
00:25:49,055 --> 00:25:51,376
It helped them figure out parts that they maybe were not

480
00:25:51,436 --> 00:25:56,217
happy with to have expert voices and identify things.

481
00:25:57,398 --> 00:26:01,379
Consultants also may have increased our budget, I know.

